PrecisAuthority to enter into AGREEMENTS with the Provinces of Alberta and Saskatchewan, CIC Industrial Interests Inc., Husky Oil Operations Ltd. and HRI, a Division of Husky Oil Operations Ltd., which provide for the sale of the federal government's interest in the Bi-Provincial heavy-oil upgrader facility located at Lloydminster, Saskatchewan.

Authority to enter into AGREEMENTS with the Provinces of Alberta and
Saskatchewan, CIC Industrial Interests Inc., Husky Oil Operations Ltd.
and HRI, a Division of Husky Oil Operations Ltd., which provide for the
sale of the federal government's interest in the Bi-Provincial heavy-oil
upgrader facility located at Lloydminster, Saskatchewan.
